reviewText: Very nice concert of best of tangerine dream songs. '

Tangerine Dream's world tour of 2012 is powerfully captured on this DVD - unfortunately it is only available in PAL format so if you don't have a multi format DVD player, you're out of luck. Too bad too because this is one smoking performance by a band that has been a favorite of mine ever since the days of the original trio back in the mid 1970s. Highly recommended!
But I can not watch this DVD, is PAL it is not for United States.  I do not have a PAL  DVD player.
